#services.section.white
  .fixed-container
    .content
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.text-left
          %h1 Our Services
          .hidden-sm.hidden-xs.service-section
            %p Writing software is more than just getting the codes to work. We take pride in building great digital products that are in rock solid condition.
            %p We rely heavily on automated test suites which allow us to craft your product with confidence, focusing on new features that matter the most.
            %p Your Idea  +  Our Best Practices  =  A World Class Software
            %a.scroll-down{href: "#contact"}
              %button.round-button
                %span
                  Launch Your Product With Us
        .col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.services-icons
          .row
            .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              %i.fa.fa-desktop.fa-3x
              %h5 WEB APPS
              %p Stunning web apps using Bootstrap or any design framework of your choice
            .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              %i.fa.fa-mobile.fa-3x
              %h5 MOBILE APPS
              %p iOS and Android native apps using React Native, the latest technology by Facebook
          .row
            .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              %i.fa.fa-server.fa-3x
              %h5 BACKEND SERVERS
              %p Backend servers/API using a popular open source framework Ruby on Rails
            .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              %i.fa.fa-code-fork.fa-3x
              %h5 WORKFLOW
              %p Setup a future-proof workflow for your newly-formed Tech team
          .row
            .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              %i.fa.fa-code.fa-3x
              %h5 TESTING
              %p If you have an app already, we can help with automated test suite to make sure your app is battle tested
            .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              %i.fa.fa-diamond.fa-3x
              %h5 YOU TELL US
              %p We are always ready to take on new challenges. Tell us your problem and we will solve it for you
          .hidden-lg.hidden-md.text-center
            %a.scroll-down{href: "#contact"}
              %button.round-button
                %span
                  Launch Your Product With Us

/ What Will You Get Section
#expectation.section
  .fixed-container
    .content.expectation
      %h1 What Will You Get
      .row
        .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
          %i.fa.fa-code.fa-4x
