          %i.fa.fa-file-text-o.fa-4x
          %h3 Documentations
          %p You will have full visibility on our processes with a well writen documentations on everything we do. Transparency is very important to us.
        .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
          %i.fa.fa-hourglass-start.fa-4x
          %h3 Save Time
          %p Spend less time worrying about the technical aspects of your business. Give us a crash course on your business and we will handle it for you.
      %a.scroll-down{href: "#contact"}
        %button.round-button
          %span
            Let's Talk

